name: DiamondsnDiamonds
overview:
DiamondsnDiamonds is an online store of UK’s leading manufacturer and wholesaler of diamond jewellery located in famous Hatton Garden, London. We are a business with a worldwide reputation of unparalleled service and decades of experience in diamonds.

The DiamondsnDiamonds philosophy is simple: Offer high-quality diamonds and fine jewellery at outstanding prices. At DiamondsnDiamonds, you’ll find the Education and guidance that make shopping easy and straightforward, so you’ll make the best decision.

Our standards of quality ensure that when you shop DiamondsnDiamonds for diamonds, you’re getting a manageable selection of diamonds. You won’t spend a lot of time sifting through jewellery that is not right for you, and we’re confident you won’t find better quality certified diamond jewellery for this price.
